e%20and%20full%20employment%20history%20are%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%20but%20are%20not%20named%20to%20protect%20their%20privacy.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20I%20interviewed%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-major-rejected-hustle-faang-jobs-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFAANG%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20software%20engineering%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20heard%20back%20from%20my%20final%20round%20within%20a%20few%20days%20and%20started%20about%20three%20weeks%20after%20signing%20the%20offer.%20I%20didn't%20stay%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company%20very%20long%20because%20the%20culture%20was%20not%20a%20fit%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-cerner-health-larry-ellison-28-billion-deadly-gamble-veterans-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOracle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20don't%20plan%20on%20leaving.%20Here's%20how%20my%20work%20experiences%20at%20both%20companies%20compare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f60f176-faa1-40b6-b786-4bf0e44acaa7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20FAANG%20company%20seemed%20more%20focused%20on%20personality%20fit%20during%20the%20interview%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20HR%20screen%20and%20a%20tech%20screen%2C%20I%20had%20a%20final%20round%20of%20four%20interviews%20back-to-back%2C%20each%20lasting%2045%20minutes.%20Three%20interviewers%20were%20senior%20engineers%2C%20and%20one%20was%20the%20hiring%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20personality%20questions%20were%20more%20detailed%20than%20the%20technical%20questions.%20They%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20I%20demonstrated%20the%20company's%20leadership%20principles%2C%20so%20they%20asked%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20tell%20me%20about%20a%20time%20you%20affected%20change%20in%20a%20company%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCan%20you%20tell%20me%20about%20a%20time%20you%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20for%20a%20customer%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technical%20questions%20were%20on%20standard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleetcode-coding-test-apple-amazon-google-technical-interview-prep-job-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeetCode%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20system%20design.%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20whiteboard%20and%20design%20a%20service%20similar%20to%20Instagram%20and%20discuss%20how%20I'd%20engineer%20it%20to%20scale%20to%20a%20billion%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d8121a5-ea06-4686-ab29-2bc1e13768c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20FAANG%20company%20sought%20candidates%20willing%20to%20work%20long%20hours%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interviewers%20didn't%20ask%20directly%20how%20long%20I%20was%20willing%20to%20work%2C%20but%20they%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BTell%20me%20about%20a%20time%20when%20you%20had%20to%20meet%20an%20aggressive%20deadline.%26quot%3B%20The%20hiring%20manager%20also%20told%20me%20the%20team%20I'd%20be%20joining%20was%20fairly%20new%20and%20wanted%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20technology%20they%20were%20developing%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20notice%20a%20few%20more%20red%20flags.%20Everyone%20I%20interviewed%20with%20had%20joined%20within%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20Most%20folks%20I%20interviewed%20with%20at%20Oracle%20had%20been%20at%20the%20company%20for%20four%20to%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20senior%20engineers%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company%20said%20it's%20fast-paced%20and%20has%20a%20work-hard%20culture%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20turnover.%20However%2C%20I'd%20also%20get%20to%20learn%20a%20lot%20and%20work%20on%20features%20that%20millions%20of%20customers%20would%20use%2C%20and%20I%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20that%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22574d127e-7c41-4d4e-9c9d-83920726e4d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20Oracle%20interview%20process%20took%20longer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20interviewed%20with%20Oracle%20in%20February%202024%20and%20started%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20steps%20were%20the%20same%2C%20but%20the%20Oracle%20process%20focused%20more%20on%20technical%20ability%20than%20the%20FAANG%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20final%20round%2C%20I%20was%20interviewed%20by%20two%20senior%20engineers%2C%20the%20hiring%20manager%2C%20and%20a%20product%20manager.%20The%20senior%20engineers%20and%20my%20hiring%20manager%20also%20asked%20me%20standard%20LeetCode%20and%20system%20design%20questions.%20My%20hiring%20manager%20asked%20if%20I%20had%20data%20center%20experience%2C%20which%20I%20didn't.%20The%20product%20manager%20asked%20me%20to%20go%20deep%20into%20the%20technical%20stuff%20I%20previously%20worked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cd0bc73-3abb-49fa-8927-66b0206cfb76%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20offer%20negotiation%20process%20was%20pretty%20similar%20for%20both%20companies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20times%2C%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-negotiate-higher-salary-better-perks-job-offer-candor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompeting%20offers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20match%20compensation.%20They%20matched%20it%20by%20increasing%20the%20amount%20of%20vested%20stock%20they'd%20give%20me%2C%20and%20I%20got%20a%2010%25%20total%20compensation%20increase%20from%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsell-rsus-as-soon-as-vest-cfp-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERSU%20vesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20spread%20evenly%20across%20four%20years.%20At%20the%20FAANG%20company%2C%20the%20four-year%20stock%20vest%20schedule%20was%205%25%20for%20year%20one%2C%2015%25%20for%20year%20two%2C%2040%25%20for%20year%20three%2C%20and%2040%25%20for%20year%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20first%20year%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company%2C%20I%20received%20a%203%25%20raise%20on%20my%20base%20pay.%20I%20haven't%20received%20a%20raise%20at%20Oracle%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0395ca6-0e75-4ef1-b520-464f5875d101%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20found%20Oracle's%20onboarding%20process%20to%20be%20much%20more%20structured%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20few%20weeks%20at%20both%20companies%20were%20spent%20getting%20access%20to%20code%20bases%2C%20familiarizing%20myself%20with%20the%20teams'%20work%2C%20and%20having%20a%20lot%20of%201%3A1%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Oracle%2C%20everyone%20helped%20explain%20the%20organization's%20overall%20mission.%20The%20team%20had%20an%20onboarding%20document%20that%20I%20could%20follow%20that%20outlined%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20structure%20or%20clear%20expectations%20in%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company.%20Management%20also%20didn't%20focus%20much%20on%20helping%20people%20get%20onboarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b92e717-d834-4cb9-86aa-26a7a306f881%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20FAANG%20coworkers%20seemed%20very%20focused%20on%20their%20level%20of%20seniority%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20single%20engineer%20I%20met%20in%20my%20first%20week%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company%20either%20asked%20me%20a%20question%20about%20how%20I%20could%20help%20them%20get%20a%20promotion%20or%20was%20very%20closed%20off%20and%20wouldn't%20communicate%20much.%20One%20midlevel%20engineer%20asked%20me%20in%20our%20first%20meeting%20whether%20I'd%20be%20open%20to%20being%20%26quot%3Bmentored%26quot%3B%20by%20him%20so%20he%20could%20use%20me%20as%20a%20data%20point%20to%20support%20his%20coming%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20engineer%20I%20met%20with%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20between%20me%20and%20my%20manager%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20about%20his%20long-term%20career%20goals%20during%20our%20first%20meeting.%20I%20asked%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-special-tests-picking-leaders-silence-skip-level-meetings-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskip-level%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20question%20about%20the%20team%2C%20and%20he%20told%20me%20my%20question%20was%20better%20suited%20for%20a%20lower-level%20manager%2C%20not%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Oracle%2C%20everyone%20was%20friendly%20and%20gave%20me%20information%20and%20advice%20on%20succeeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229769819d-341e-458b-ba70-8d9ed95daafb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOracle%20has%20a%20sense%20of%20teamwork%20and%20collaboration%20that%20the%20FAANG%20company%20did%20not%20have%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20micromanagement%20is%20virtually%20nonexistent%20at%20Oracle.%20Management%20and%20executives%20allow%20engineers%20and%20other%20contributors%20to%20set%20their%20own%20deadlines%20and%20expectations.%20I%20felt%20trusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20culture%20at%20the%20FAANG%20company%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20I've%20been%20part%20of.%20My%20teammates%20and%20I%20regularly%20worked%20until%20late%20into%20the%20night%2C%20and%20there%20was%20lots%20of%20micromanagement%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20left.%20It%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20lower-level%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20affected%20both%20my%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%20My%20sleep%20pattern%20was%20chaotic%2C%20and%20I%20skipped%20a%20lot%20of%20meals%20because%20of%20the%20constant%20stress%20and%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2140301-d047-4c5d-bd62-cdcd8b5a06f7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESince%20I%20left%20the%20FAANG%20company%20for%20Oracle%2C%20I%20haven't%20looked%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20straw%20was%20when%20the%20FAANG%20company%20asked%20me%20to%20relocate%20to%20a%20different%20state%20with%20three-months%20notice.%20I%20told%20my%20manager%20I'd%20move%20but%20immediately%20started%20searching%2