0be%20bearish%20on%20US%20equities%2C%20full%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemple%20sees%207%25-8%25%20annualized%20returns%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20In%20the%20near%20term%20within%20the%20US%2C%20energy%20and%20financials%20stocks%20should%20have%20an%20upside%20given%20that%20they'd%20get%20a%20boost%20from%20deregulation%20and%20corporate%20tax%20cuts%20that%20could%20come%20under%20the%20incoming%20Trump%20administration%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Temple%20highlighted%20a%20couple%20of%20opportunities%20outside%20the%20US%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20emerging%20markets%20ex-China%20are%20trading%20at%20discount%20valuations%2C%20and%20could%20be%20set%20to%20become%20even%20cheaper%20if%20Trump's%20trade%20policy%20ends%20up%20being%20more%20hardline%20than%20investors%20expect.%20The%20iShares%20MSCI%20Emerging%20Markets%20ex%20China%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-msci-emerging-markets-ex-china-etf-us46434g7640%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEMXC%3C%2Fa%3E)%20trades%20at%20a%2016.8%20trailing%2012-month%20PE%20ratio%2C%20while%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20sits%20just%20below%20a%2030%20PE%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20Temple%20likes%20EMs%20outside%20of%20China%20is%20the%20growing%20polarization%20of%20China%20and%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20worsening%20investment%20climate%20in%20China%20that's%20starting%20to%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%2015%20to%2020%20years%2C%20all%20the%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20into%20EM%20went%20into%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20five%20quarters%2C%20we've%20now%20had%20three%20quarters%20of%20negative%20FDI%20in%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20is%20a%20significant%20reallocation%20away%20from%20China%20into%20other%20EMs%20that%20are%20more%20closely%20aligned%20with%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Temple%20likes%20Japanese%20stocks%2C%20which%20trade%20at%20similar%20valuation%20levels%20to%20EM%20ex-China.%20He%20said%20the%20country's%20economic%20situation%20should%20continue%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan%20still%20has%20the%20structural%20problems%20and%20demographics%20and%20too%20much%20debt%20that%20they%20had%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Temple%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20look%20at%20Japan%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20really%20in%20the%20early%20innings%20of%20a%20normalization%20around%20inflation%20and%20wages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20should%20also%20benefit%20from%20the%20US-China%20trade%20war%20as%20well%2C%20Temple%20said.%20His%20bullish%20outlook%20extends%20over%20the%20next%20three-to-five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20trusted%20ally%2C%26quot%3B%20Temple%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20happy%20to%20source%20sophisticated%20technological%20equipment%20from%20Japan%20as%20a%20safe%20provider.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Matthews%20Japan%20Active%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fmatthews-japan-active-etf-us5771305944%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPAN%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20the%20iShares%20MSCI%20Japan%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-msci-japan-etf-us46434g8226%3FmiRedirects%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEWJ%3C%2Fa%3E)%20are%20examples%20of%20funds%20that%20offer%20exposure%20to%20Japanese%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-stock-market-tips-sp500-outlook-lazard-temple-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736328602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677c575e4fdf00939ed68215%3Fformat%3Djpeg%2