ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta's%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20for%20platform%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ad%20agency%20veteran%20told%20BI.%20They%20and%20some%20others%20interviewed%20asked%20for%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20business%20relationships%3B%20their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20reaction%20%E2%80%94%20or%20lack%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20reflects%20both%20advertisers'%20reliance%20on%20Meta%20and%20the%20shifting%20conversation%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scared-of-culture-war-controversy-its-hurting-media-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20brands%20should%20approach%20%26quot%3Bbrand%20safety%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%26quot%3Bsuitability%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20refer%20to%20when%20marketers%20try%20to%20avoid%20funding%20or%20appearing%20next%20to%20content%20they%20deem%20unsuitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20brands%20have%20shied%20away%20from%20platforms%20that%20are%20too%20tied%20to%20news%20or%20controversy%2C%20mostly%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20cancel%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Toni%20Box%2C%20EVP%20of%20brand%20experience%20at%20the%20media%20agency%20Assembly.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20some%20point%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ask%3A%20Are%20we%20missing%20opportunities%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20during%20meaningful%20moments%20because%20we%20don't%20trust%20audiences%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20news%20story%20and%20an%20ad%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229712840f-9c52-40bd-8b91-1ace7e363f6e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20brand-safety%20tides%20are%20shifting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20used%20to%20bend%20over%20backward%20to%20address%20advertisers'%20brand-safety%20concerns.%20But%20brands%20weren't%20mentioned%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E's%20video%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-community-notes-third-party-fact-checkers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20changes%20or%20in%20policy%20chief%20Joel%20Kaplan's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-zuckerberg-content-moderation-california-texas-censorship-bias-musk-x-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%20with%20Fox%20News'%20%26quot%3BFox%20and%20Friends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20their%20pitch%20was%20about%20preventing%20the%20censorship%20of%20speech.%20Meta%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-community-notes-third-party-fact-checkers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplace%20third-party%20fact-checkers%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20community-based%20fact-checking%20program%2C%20addressing%20criticism%20that%20the%20previous%20system%20was%20too%20partisan%20and%20was%20often%20overcorrective.%20The%20company%20also%20said%20it%20would%20loosen%20some%20content%20moderation%20restrictions%20on%20topics%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20mainstream%20discourse%26quot%3B%20and%20be%20more%20open%20to%20reintroducing%20political%20content%20to%20people's%20feeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20did%20give%20a%20very%20brief%20public%20nod%20to%20advertisers.%20A%20Meta%20spokesperson%20pointed%20BI%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7282394551011426304%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Meta%20ads%20exec%20Nicola%20Mendelsohn%20that%20said%20the%20company%20continued%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20brand%20safety%20and%20suitability%20by%20offering%20a%20suite%20of%20tools%20for%20advertisers.%20In%20an%20email%20from%20Meta%20account%20reps%20to%20ad%20buyers%2C%20copies%20of%20which%20were%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20knew%20how%20important%20it%20was%20to%20continue%20giving%20advertisers%20transparency%20and%20control%20over%20their%20brand%20suitability.%20And%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-influenced-meta-ditching-fact-checkers-cmo-alex-schultz-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Meta's%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20Alex%20Schultz%20said%20advertisers'%20primary%20brand%20safety%20concerns%20were%20around%20hate%20speech%20and%20adult%20nudity%20and%20that%20its%20tools%20would%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bprecision%20and%20not%20be%20taking%20down%20things%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20taking%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20private%20grumbling%20from%20some%20advertisers%20about%20the%20changes%2C%20and%20how%20they%20appeared%20to%20be%20timed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-donald-trump-moderation-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappease%20incoming%20President%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20industry%20insiders%20said%20they%20don't%20expect%20much%20public%20blowback%20on%20Meta.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertiser%20boycotts%20and%20similar%20actions%20were%20once%20seen%20as%20a%20point%20of%20leverage%20for%20marketers.%20One%20high-profile%20example%20was%20the%202020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-facebook-not-gonna-change-due-to-advertising-boycott-report-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23StopHateFor%20Profit%3C%2Fa%3E%20movement%20when%20hundreds%20of%20major%20brands%20protested%20Meta's%20policies%20on%20hate%20speech%20and%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20brand%20safety%20has%20recently%20become%20a%20political%20hot%20potato%20and%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scared-of-culture-war-controversy-its-hurting-media-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflash%20point%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20some%20influential%2C%20right-leaning%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20House%20Judiciary%20Committee%2C%20Jim%20Jordan%2C%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-judiciary-committee-probe-garm-brand-safety-conservative-media-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigating%3C%2Fa%3E%20whether%20advertisers%20had%20illegally%20colluded%20to%20demonetize%20conservative%20platforms%20and%20voices.%20Elon%20Musk's%20X%20went%20on%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.txnd.393003%2Fgov.uscourts.txnd.393003.1.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esue%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20for%20Responsible%20Media%2C%20the%20brand-safety%20initiative%20at%20the%20center%20of%20Jordan's%20investigation%2C%20and%20some%20of%20its%20advertiser%20members%20after%20they%20withdrew%20ad%20dollars%20from%20the%20platform.%20GARM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fad-group-to-suspend-garm-initiative-following-elon-musk-lawsuit-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscontinued%3C%2Fa%3E%20activities%20days%20later.%20Jordan%20has%20continued%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adweek.com%2Fagencies%2Freport-omnicom-ipg-deal-probed-by-congress-over-ties-to-garm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%3C%2Fa%3E%20advertisers%20about%20their%20involvement%20in%20GARM%2C%20and%20X's%20litigation%20against%20it%20and%20some%20of%20its%20members%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20media%20agency%20employee%20told%20BI%20that%20they%20had%20clients%20who%20were%20now%20more%20cautious%20about%20criticizing%20platforms%20in%20public%20or%20saying%20they%20would%20pull%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20analysts%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%94%20politics%20aside%20%E2%80%94%20many%20marketers%20would%20likely%20continue%20to%20spend%20with%20Meta%20so%20long%20as%20it%20delivered%20them%20the%20audiences%20and%20ad%20performance%20they%20had%20come%20to%20expect.%20Meta%20commands%20about%2021%25%20of%20the%20US%20digital%20ad%20market%2C%20behind%20only%20Google%2C%20according%20to%20data%20firm%20EMARKETER.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20after%20Google%2C%20Meta%20is%20the%20next-best%20performer%20as%20far%20as%20ROI%20is%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shamsul%20Chowdhury%2C%20VP%20of%20paid%20social%20at%20the%20digital%20ad%20agency%20Jellyfish%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20advertisers%20get%20from%20their%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e589d7d-c7b1-46f4-a886-1276a3b610f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvertisers%20are%20split%20on%20whether%20the%20changes%20will%20improve%20Meta's%20platforms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advertisers%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%20said%20they%20had%20outstanding%20questions%20about%20the%20new%20thresholds%20Meta%20would%20apply%20to%20removing%20posts%2C%20what's%20on%20the%20road%20map%20for%20monitoring%20trends%20around%20misinformation%2C%20and%20whether%20they%20would%20still%20be%20able%20to%20effectively%20apply%20their%20own%20third-party%20brand%20suitability%20software%20to%20content%20on%20Meta's%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20said%20they%20would%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20how%20Meta's%20Community%20Notes-like%20feature%20would%20work%20in%20practice%2C%20especially%20as%20some%20hadn't%20been%20impressed%20with%20X's%20performance%20in%20this%20area%20with%20a%20similar%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20major%20step%20back%20and%20likely%20going%20to%20result%20in%20serious%20issues%20where%20social%20platforms%2C%20not%20just%20Meta%2C%20are%20going%20to%20hide%20behind%20the%20notion%20that%20their%20users%20do%20the%20moderation%20and%20fact-checking%20for%20them%20and%20they%20are%20free%20speech%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ruben%20Schreurs%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20marketing%20consultancy%20Ebiquity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20entirely%20clear%20how%20effective%20X's%20Community%20Notes%20have%20been.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2307.07960%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20last%20year%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20University%20of%20Melbourne%2C%20and%20JLU%20Giessen%20concluded%20that%20X's%20%26quot%3BCommunity%20Notes%20might%20be%20too%20slow%20to%20effectively%20reduce%20engagement%20with%20misinformation%20in%20the%20early%20(and%20most%20viral)%20stage%20of%20diffusion.%26quot%3B%20Still%2C%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Ffullarticle%2F2818054%3FguestAccessKey%3D293a59ac-c25a-4267-bf73-98cd74fc978f%26utm_source%3DFor_The_Media%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_campaign%3Dftm_links%26utm_content%3Dtfl%26utm_term%3D042424%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Qualcomm%20Institute%20within%20UC%20San%20Diego%20found%20Community%20Notes%20helped%20counter%20false%20information%20about%20Covid%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advertising%20execs%20supported%20Meta's%20announcement.%20Two%20media%20agency%20reps%20said%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20conversations%20people%20are%20having%20on%20the%20platform%20could%20benefit%20Meta%20and%20advertisers%20alike%20by%20boosting%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20best%20news%20is%20free%20speech%20and%20mitigation%20of%20harmful%20or%20dangerous%20content%20remains%20the%20primary%20focus%20of%20this%20maturing%20program%2C%20and%20Meta%20has%20taken%20a%20forward%20position%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Donahue%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20digital%20media%20consultancy%20Up%20and%20to%20the%20Right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Zaneis%20of%20the%20ad%20initiative%20the%20Trustworthy%20Accountability%20Group%20said%20Meta's%20announcement%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20evolution%20of%20the%20platform's%20brand-safety%20standards%20and%20not%20a%20retreat%20from%20protecting%20users%20and%20marketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20speed%20and%20accuracy%20of%20the%20Community%20Notes%20tool%20is%20impressive%20and%20it's%20the%20increased%20transparency%20that%20makes%20a%20fundamental%20difference%20for%20users%20and%20marketers%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20Zeneis%20said%20of%20X's%20implementation%20of%20the%20concept%20so%20far.%20%26quot%3BIf%20something%20seems%20to%20be%20working%2C%20we%20shouldn't%20discourage%20others%20from%20adopting%20the%20approach%20just%20because%20it%20hasn't%20been%20precisely%20tested.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-content-moderation-update-impact-ad-business-brand-safety-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736328301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677d9aeef83fcec7e5b4ee4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-content-moderation-update-impact-ad-business-brand-safety-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta's%20content-moderation%20changes%20have%20sparked%20concerns%20over%20its%20brand-safety%20commitments%2C%20but%20advertisers%20are%20unlikely%20to%20pull%20spending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-content-moderation-update-impact-ad-business-brand-safety-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Don't%20kill%20golden%20goose'%3A%20Kaif%20on%20Bumrah%20as%20captain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736328122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117050062%2Cimgsize-21458.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Fdont-kill-the-golden-goose-former-india-batter-urges-caution-in-appointing-jasprit-bumrah-as-captain%2Farticleshow%2F117050074.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%20captained%20the%20Indian%20team%20during%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20a%20victory%20in%20Perth%20but%20suffering%20a%20loss%20in%20Sydney.%20With%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Test%20career%20in%20doubt%2C%20there%20are%20discussions%20about%20Bumrah%20as%20the%20full-time%20Test%20captain.%20However%2C%20Mohammad%20Kaif%20has%20suggested%20that%20this%20added%20responsibility%20could%20put%20extra%20pressure%20on%20the%20fast%20bowler.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Fdont-kill-the-golden-goose-former-india-batter-urges-caution-in-appointing-jasprit-bumrah-as-captain%2Farticleshow%2F117050074.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sobha's%20Q3%20results%3A%20Sales%20plunge%2029%25%20YoY%2C%20B'luru%20accounts%20for%20most%20sales%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736327591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fsobha-s-q3-results-sales-plunge-29-yoy-b-luru-accounts-for-most-sales-125010800584_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sobha's%20new%20sales%20during%20the%20quarter%20spanned%20an%20area%20of%201.01%20million%20square%20feet%20(msf)%20at%20an%20average%20price%20realisation%20of%20Rs%2013%2C663%20per%20square%20foot%20(sq%20ft)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fsobha-s-q3-results-sales-plunge-29-yoy-b-luru-accounts-for-most-sales-125010800584_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20One%20Knew%20What%20To%20Do%26quot%3B%3A%20California%20Wildfire%20Sparks%20Evacuation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20ferocious%20wildfire%20in%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20suburb%20devoured%20buildings%20and%20sparked%20panicked%20evacuations%20Tuesday%2C%20as%20hurricane-force%20winds%20tore%20through%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrightened%20residents%20abandoned%20their%20cars%20on%20one%20of%20the%20only%20roads%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20upscale%20Pacific%20Palisades%20area%2C%20fleeing%20on%20foot%20from%20the%20almost%203%2C000-acre%20(1%2C200-hectare)%20blaze%20engulfing%20an%20area%20packed%20with%20multimillion-dollar%20homes%20in%20the%20Santa%20Monica%20Mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirefighters%20used%20bulldozers%20to%20push%20dozens%20of%20vehicles%20--%20including%20expensive%20models%20like%20BMWs%2C%20Teslas%20and%20Mercedes%20--%20to%20one%20side%2C%20leaving%20many%20crumpled%20and%20with%20their%20alarms%20blaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20Fire%20Department%20Chief%20Kristin%20Crowley%20said%20despite%20the%20chaotic%20evacuation%2C%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20reports%20of%20any%20deaths%20or%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20firefighters%20swarmed%20the%20area%2C%20attacking%20the%20blaze%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20from%20the%20air%2C%20while%20crews%20worked%20in%20steep%20terrain%20to%20cut%20back%20vegetation%20and%20create%20firebreaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2030%2C000%20people%20were%20ordered%20to%20evacuate%20the%20fast-spreading%20flames%2C%20which%20leveled%20multiple%20homes%20as%20powerful%20winds%20spread%20embers%20far%20and%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20out%20of%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Fire%20Chief%20Anthony%20Marrone%2C%20speaking%20at%20an%20afternoon%20press%20conference%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20winds%20are%20expected%20to%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20town%2C%20on%20the%20northern%20edge%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20another%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20Eaton%20Canyon%2C%20near%20Pasadena%2C%20quickly%20consuming%20200%20acres%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20according%20to%20Angeles%20National%20Forest%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Everyone%20panicked'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20erupted%20midmorning%20and%20swelled%20quickly%2C%20taking%20many%20residents%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20man%2C%20who%20gave%20his%20name%20as%20Gary%2C%20told%20broadcaster%20KTLA%20hot%20ashes%20were%20raining%20down%20on%20his%20community%20of%20Sea%20Ridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20smoke%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20and%20I%20was%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20not%20come%20over%20the%20hill...%20Five%20minutes%20later%2C%20it's%20coming%20down%20the%20hill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20panicked%2C%20that's%20when%20everybody%20made%20a%20run%20and%20went%20to%20go%20and%20pack%20their%20houses%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvacuee%20Kelsey%20Trainor%20said%20she%20saw%20the%20fire%20explode%20in%20size%20as%20she%20was%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20hill%2C%20which%20is%20about%20two%20or%20three%20miles%2C%20there%20were%20flames%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20road%2C%20and%20it%20became%20gridlocked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knew%20what%20to%20do.%20Everyone%20was%20honking%20their%20horns.%20There's%20flames%20all%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20see%20people%20walking%20with%20suitcases%2C%20with%20their%20dogs%2C%20children.%20An%20elderly%20woman%20was%20really%20visibly%20upset%20and%20in%20tears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacific%20Palisades%20resident%20Andrew%20Hires%20told%20AFP%20he%20got%20a%20text%20alerting%20him%20to%20the%20fire%20as%20his%20child%20was%20at%20the%20dentist%20about%20to%20have%20a%20tooth%20extracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pulled%20off%20the%20mask%20and%20ran%20to%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20rough%20night'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20came%20as%20the%20area%20was%20being%20hit%20by%20seasonal%20Santa%20Ana%20winds%20that%20forecasters%20said%20could%20develop%20into%20the%20worst%20windstorm%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20with%20gusts%20of%20up%20to%20100%20miles%20(160%20kilometers)%20an%20hour%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20looks%20pretty%2C%20pretty%20concerning%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20meteorologist%20Daniel%20Swain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%2C%20I%20think%2C%20a%20rough%20night.%20And%20what's%20going%20on%20now%20is%20only%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%20because%20weather%20conditions%20are%20going%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20huge%20pall%20of%20smoke%20visible%20over%20the%20whole%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20events%20throughout%20the%20area%20were%20cancelled%2C%20including%20a%20red-carpet%20premiere%20of%20Jennifer%20Lopez's%20new%20film%20%26quot%3BUnstoppable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20--%20who%20was%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20a%20planned%20announcement%20on%20new%20national%20monuments%20--%20was%20briefed%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20has%20approved%20federal%20aid%20to%20help%20California%20tackle%20the%20blaze%2C%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20politics%2C%20no%20hand%20wringing%2C%20no%20kissing%20the%20feet.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20said%2C%20'Yes.%20What%20else%20do%20you%20need%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncoming%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20previously%20threatened%20to%20withhold%20wildfire%20aid%20from%20Democrat-run%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWildfires%20are%2