0donated%20to%20Trump's%20inaugural%20fund.%20Zuckerberg%20has%20done%20that%20and%20more%2C%20including%20visiting%20Mar-a-Lago%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20the%20president%20elect%2C%20naming%20close%20Trump%20ally%20and%20UFC%20CEO%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fufc-ceo-dana-white-join-meta-board-directors-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDana%20White%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Meta's%20board%2C%20and%20promoting%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-joel-kaplan-trump-nick-clegg-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJoel%20Kaplan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20longtime%20Republican%20lobbyist%20to%20chief%20global%20affairs%20officer.%20(On%20Tuesday%20Kaplan%20gave%20an%20interview%20on%20Fox%20and%20Friends%20to%20promote%20the%20company's%20content%20moderation%20changes.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20meant%20to%20quell%20a%20once%20adversarial%20relationship%20between%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Trump%2C%20who%20had%20threatened%20to%20jail%20Zuckerberg%20if%20his%20social%20sites%20interfered%20with%20the%202024%20election%2C%20and%20years%20ago%20accused%20Facebook%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Banti-Trump%26quot%3B%20and%20colluding%20against%20him%20(Zuckerberg%20pushed%20back%20against%20such%20claims).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20my%20colleague%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpost%2Fpreview%3Fsvapi%26post_id%3D677d44f165b92a8f4ac7963a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3EPeter%20Kafka%20wrote%20of%20the%20community%20notes%20news%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20to%20see%20Zuckerberg's%20moves%20as%20anything%20other%20than%20a%20straightforward%20attempt%20to%20please%20Trump%20and%20the%20incoming%20president's%20conservative%20allies%2C%20who%20have%20often%20complained%20that%20Zuckerberg's%20properties%20were%20biased%20against%20them.%26quot%3B%20Even%20Trump%20said%20Tuesday%20that%20Meta%20is%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mark-zuckerberg-threats-meta-political-content-changes-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cu%3Eprobably%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3B%20responding%20to%20his%20own%20past%20threats%20against%20Zuck%20by%20pivoting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20fact%20checkers%20who%20will%20soon%20be%20dismissed%20by%20Meta%20began%20with%20a%20program%20in%20December%202016%2C%20after%20Facebook%20faced%20harsh%20criticism%20for%20its%20role%20in%20spreading%20misinformation%20in%20Trump's%20first%20election%20a%20month%20prior.%20Meta%20actively%20worked%20to%20downplay%20political%20content%20following%20the%20January%206%20insurrection%2C%20and%20suspended%20Trump%20from%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20(Meta%20lifted%20the%20suspension%20in%20early%202023%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20public%20should%20be%20able%20to%20access%20what%20politicians%20are%20saying.%20The%20move%20came%20shortly%20after%20Musk%20allowed%20Trump%20back%20on%20Twitter).%20When%20Meta%20launched%20Threads%2C%20its%20own%20Twitter%20competitor%2C%20in%202023%2C%20Instagram%20head%20Adam%20Mosseri%20said%20the%20new%20app%20would%20not%20encourage%20breaking%20news%20and%20politics%20posts.%20But%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20rebuilt%20X%20in%20his%20own%20image%20to%20favor%20conservative%20and%20far-right%20accounts%2C%20has%20found%20a%20social%20media%20site%20that%20can%20win%20when%20embracing%20the%20president.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Meta%20also%20said%20it%20will%20reverse%20course%20and%20stop%20downgrading%20political%20content%2C%20and%20start%20phasing%20politics%20back%20into%20users'%20feeds.%20(A%20Meta%20spokesperson%20referred%20to%20past%20public%20statements%2C%20but%20did%20not%