nce%20Gooden%20has%20called%20out%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20decision%20to%20probe%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani's%20companies%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20move%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Democratic%20tenure%20aimed%20at%20disruption%20before%20Donald%20Trump's%20inauguration.%20In%20a%20strongly%20worded%20letter%20to%20Attorney%20General%20Merric%20B%20Garland%2C%20he%20questioned%20the%20need%20for%20the%20move%20that%20risks%20straining%20America's%20global%20alliances%20and%20advised%20the%20Justice%20Department%20to%20focus%20on%20punishing%20bad%20actors%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20Adani%20Group%20and%20senior%20officials%20from%20his%20conglomerate%20were%20indicted%20in%20November%20for%20allegedly%20defrauding%20US%20investors%20by%20concealing%20a%20bribery%20scheme%20to%20secure%20Indian%20government%20contracts.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20had%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20as%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gooden%20has%20accused%20the%20Justice%20Department%20of%20being%20ignorant%20of%20the%20rising%20violent%20crimes%20in%20the%20country%20and%20targeting%20businesses%20for%20alleged%20wrongdoings%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20Adani%20case%2C%20he%20said%20that%20even%20if%20the%20allegations%20are%20proven%20true%2C%20it%20would%20still%20fail%20to%20make%20the%20US%20the%20appropriate%20and%20final%20arbiter%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbribe%26quot%3B%20was%20allegedly%20paid%20to%20Indian%20government%20officials%20in%20India.%20Rather%2C%20disrespecting%20India's%20authority%20can%20permanently%20damage%20the%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20important%20allies%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-lawmaker-challenges-biden-administration-over-adani-charges-full-text-7425147%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EClick%20here%20for%20full%20text%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUS%20Lawmaker%20Challenges%20Biden%20Administration%20Over%20Adani%20Charges%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20respecting%20India's%20authority%20over%20this%20matter%20could%20strain%20and%20even%20permanently%20damage%20our%20international%20relations%20with%20a%20strategically%20important%20and%20key%20economic%20and%20political%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20reliable%20partners%20America%20has%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%2C%20alongside%20being%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20and%20largest%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20Such%20reckless%20acts%20of%20pursuit%20against%20its%20top%20industrialists%20could%20start%20a%20harmful%20narrative%20against%20India's%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congressman%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20Attorney%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmaker%20said%20that%20targeting%20entities%20that%20invest%20billions%20in%20the%20US%20and%20create%20jobs%20for%20Americans%20harms%20them%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20forego%20real%20threats%20from%20violent%20crime%2C%20economic%20espionage%2C%20and%20CCP%20influence%20and%20go%20after%20those%20who%20contribute%20to%20our%20economic%20growth%2C%20it%20discourages%20valuable%20new%20investors%20hopeful%20of%20investing%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGooden%20also%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%20suggesting%20that%20it%20is%20aimed%20at%20disruption%20before%20Donald%20Trump%20takes%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-detail-in-chargesheet-over-who-has-been-bribed-senior-lawyer-mukul-rohatgi-on-us-charges-against-adani-group-7115038%5C%22%3EMukul%20Rohatgi%20Punches%20Holes%20In%20US%20Indictment%20Linked%20To%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20unwelcome%20and%20politically%20charged%20atmosphere%20for%20investors%20will%20only%20stall%20efforts%20to%20revitalize%20America's%20industrial%20base%20and%20economic%20growth%2C%20directly%20undermine%20President%20Trump's%20commitment%20to%20revive%20the%20economy%20with%20increased%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congressman%20also%20called%20out%20the%20Justice%20Department%20for%20not%20acting%20against%20American%20executives%20who%20had%20allegedly%20laundered%20money%20and%20paid%20bribes%20to%20foreign%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20also%20included%20a%20five-pointer%20questionnaire%20related%20to%20the%20Adani%20case%2C%20including%20why%20the%20Justice%20Department%20had%20not%20indicted%20a%20single%20American%20if%20the%20case%20involved%20a%20nexus%20with%20the%20US.%20Stating%20that%20since%20the%20parties%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20case%20are%20in%20India%2C%20he%20asked%20if%20they%20are%20seeking%20to%20enforce%20justice%20in%20India%20and%20whether%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20seek%20an%20extradition%20of%20the%20Indian%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20DOJ's%20contingency%20plan%20if%20India%20refuses%20to%20comply%20with%20an%20extradition%20request%20and%20claim%20sole%20authority%20over%20this%20case%3F%20Is%20the%20DOJ%20or%20the%20Biden%20administration%20willing%20to%20escalate%20this%20case%20into%20an%20international%20incident%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20ally%20like%20India%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20further%20asked%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20questions%20flagged%20the%20probable%20consequences%20of%20its%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736319240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fo4qn0778_george-soros-biden_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-lawmaker-lance-gooden-rips-into-us-char