3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EU.S.%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E950%20Pennsylvania%20Avenue%20NW%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2020530%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDear%20Attorney%20General%20Garland%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20am%20writing%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20(DOJ)%20recent%20selective%20pursuits%20of%20cases%20against%20foreign%20entities%20that%20could%20irreparably%20strain%20America's%20global%20alliances.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20our%20country%20enters%20a%20new%20period%20under%20President%20Trump%2C%20Americans%20are%20hopeful%20it%20will%20mark%20the%20revival%20of%20prosperity%2C%20growth%2C%20economic%20recovery%2C%20and%20political%20freedom.%20An%20important%20factor%20in%20our%20quest%20to%20revive%20our%20country's%20prosperity%20includes%20the%20ability%20and%20freedom%20of%20prospective%20investors%20to%20do%20business%20in%20America.%20In%20complete%20abeyance%20of%20public%20outcry%20about%20the%20rising%20violent%20crimes%20at%20home%2C%20the%20DOJ%20seems%20to%20be%20pursuing%20new%20expeditions%20to%20target%20businesses%20for%20alleged%20injustices%20abroad.%20One%20such%20example%20is%20the%20recent%20indictment%20of%20an%20Indian%20company's%20executives%20for%20alleged%20acts%20conducted%20in%20India%20in%20United%20States%20v.%20Adani%20(the%20Adani%20case)%20before%20the%20United%20States%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Eastern%20District%20of%20New%20York.1%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20allegations%20in%20the%20Adani%20case%2C%20even%20if%20proven%20true%2C%20would%20still%20fail%20to%20make%20us%20the%20appropriate%20and%20final%20arbiter%20on%20the%20issue.%20These%20%26quot%3Bbribes%26quot%3B%20were%20allegedly%20paid%20to%20Indian%20state%20government%20officials%2C%20in%20India%2C%20by%20Indian%20executives%20of%20an%20Indian%20company%2C%20with%20no%20concrete%20involvement%20of%20or%20injury%20to%20any%20American%20party.%20Conversely%2C%20Smartmatic%2C%20an%20American%20company%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20our%20elections%2C%20had%20executives%20who%20allegedly%20laundered%20money%20and%20paid%20bribes%20to%20foreign%20governments%2C%20according%20to%20the%20DOJ's%20indictment%20earlier.%20However%2C%20despite%20numerous%20attempts%20by%20my%20colleagues%20and%20I%20to%20have%20our%20concerns%20addressed%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20we%20were%20never%20briefed%20by%20your%20department.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EConsidering%20the%20highly%20selective%20nature%20of%20these%20pursuits%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20understand%20the%20wisdom%20guiding%20some%20of%20the%20decisions%20surrounding%20the%20Adani%20case%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.1.%20Why%20has%20the%20DOJ%20not%20indicted%20a%20single%20American%20if%20the%20case%20involves%20a%20significant%20nexus%20with%20the%20United%20States%3F%20Were%20there%20no%20Americans%20involved%20in%20this%20alleged%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.2.%20Why%20has%20the%20DOJ%20pursued%20this%20case%20against%20Gautam%20Adani%20when%20the%20alleged%20criminal%20act%2C%20and%20the%20parties%20allegedly%20involved%20are%20in%20India%3F%20Do%20you%20seek%20to%20enforce%20justice%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.3.%20Will%20the%20DOJ%20seek%20an%20extradition%20of%20the%20Indian%20executives%20involved%20in%20this%20case%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.4.%20What%20is%20the%20DOJ's%20contingency%20plan%20if%20India%20refuses%20to%20comply%20with%20an%20extradition%20request%20and%20claim%20sole%20authority%20over%20this%20case%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ.5.%20Is%20the%20DOJ%20or%20the%20Biden%20administration%20willing%20to%20escalate%20this%20case%20into%20an%20international%20incident%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20ally%20like%20India%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThese%20questions%20are%20also%20here%20to%20remind%20you%20of%20the%20probable%20consequences%20of%20these%20actions.%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20reliable%20partners%20America%20has%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20region%2C%20alongside%20being%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20and%20largest%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20Such%20reckless%20acts%20of%20pursuit%20against%20its%20top%20industrialists%20could%20start%20a%20harmful%20narrative%20against%20India's%20growth.%20Not%20respecting%20India's%20authority%20over%20this%20matter%20could%20strain%20and%20even%20permanently%20damage%20our%20international%20relations%20with%20a%20strategically%20important%20and%20key%20economic%20and%20political%20ally.%20At%20this%20juncture%2C%20letting%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20investigate%2C%20determine%20any%20injury%2C%20and%20adjudicate%20on%20the%20matter%20instead%20of%20jumping%20to%20premature%20conclusions%20would%20be%20the%20best%20and%20only%20appropriate%20course%20of%20action.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20wise%20to%20pursue%20cases%20where%20the%20department%20is%20certain%20we%20have%20appropriate%20and%20conclusive%20jurisdiction%2C%20aside%20from%20a%20serious%20shot%20at%20winning.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETargeting%20entities%20who%20invest%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20create%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20for%20Americans%20only%20harms%20us%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20When%20we%20forego%20real%20threats%20from%20violent%20crime%2C%20economic%20espionage%2C%20and%20CCP%20influence%20and%20go%20after%20those%20who%20contribute%20to%20our%20economic%20growth%2C%20it%20discourages%20valuable%20new%20investors%20hopeful%20of%20investing%20in%20our%20country.%20An%20unwelcome%20and%20politically%20charged%20atmosphere%20for%20investors%20will%20only%20stall%20efforts%20to%20revitalize%20America's%20industrial%20base%20and%20economic%20growth%2C%20directly%20undermine%20President%20Trump's%20commitment%20to%20revive%20the%20economy%20with%20increased%20investments.%20Given%20the%20timing%20of%20these%20decisions%20coincides%20with%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20concerns%20arise%20that%20the%20only%20true%20goal%20here%20is%20disruption%20for%20President%20Trump.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInstead%20of%20expending%20valuable%20taxpayer%20resources%20on%20opening%20lengthy%2C%20and%20perhaps%20politically%20motivated%20pursuits%20in%20foreign%20countries%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20the%20Department%20should%20co-operate%20with%20the%20incoming%20administration%20on%20better%20serving%20the%20American%20people.%20As%20a%20cog%20in%20the%20outgoing%20administration%2C%20it%20is%20your%20duty%20to%20the%20public%20in%20being%20mindful%20of%20not%20creating%20further%20complications%20that%20could%20compromise%20America's%20geopolitical%20eminence.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20above%20questions%2C%20please%20also%20report%20if%20there%20has%20been%20any%20communication%20or%20negotiation%20regarding%20the%20Adani%20case%20between%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20(including%20any%20of%20its%20agents%2C%20subsidiaries%2C%20instrumentalities%2C%20or%20authorized%20representatives)%20and%20any%20third-party%20or%20agent%20representing%20any%20third%20party%20that%20works%20closely%2C%20for%2C%20or%20in%20conjunction%20with%20any%20entity%20partly%20owned%20or%20controlled%20by%20George%20Soros.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20ask%20for%20your%20complete%20and%20thorough%20cooperation%20in%20this%20matter%20and%20request%20the%20DOJ%20promptly%20and%20properly%20responds%20to%20this%20letter%20no%20later%20than%20January%2031%2C%202025.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELance%20Hooden%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMember%20of%20Congress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20