%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20Canada!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F113789874318969723%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20hours%20after%20Donald%20Trump%20renewed%20his%20offer%20of%20making%20Canada%20the%2051st%20state%20of%20America%20and%20threatened%20to%20use%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20force%26quot%3B%20to%20absorb%20Canada%20into%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20Florida%20Mar-a%20Lago%20home%20hours%20after%20his%20election%20victory%20was%20certified%2C%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20get%20rid%20of%20that%20artificially%20drawn%20line%2C%20and%20you%20take%20a%20look%20at%20what%20that%20looks%20like%2C%20and%20it%20would%20also%20be%20much%20better%20for%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanada%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20that%20would%20really%20be%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20Canada's%20military%20spending%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20very%20small%20military.%20They%20rely%20on%20our%20military.%20It's%20all%20fine%2C%20but%2C%20you%20know%2C%20they%20got%20to%20pay%20for%20that.%20It's%20very%20unfair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20would%20use%20military%20force%20to%20bring%20Canada%20to%20heel%2C%20the%20incoming%20president%20said%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20economic%20force.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPromising%20to%20%26quot%3Bturn%20the%20economy%20around%20very%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20approaching%20the%20dawn%20of%20America's%20golden%20age.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20hit%20back%20at%20Trump's%20threat%2C%20saying%2