ys%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20oil%20processing%20unit%20and%20office%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523.jpg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20given%20me%20financial%20stability%2C%20pride%20in%20my%20work%2C%20and%20a%20brighter%20future%20for%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramavtar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20farmer.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20farmer%20with%20divided%20land%20and%20unpredictable%20income%2C%20life%20was%20tough.%20I%20struggled%20to%20provide%20for%20my%20family%20and%20lacked%20opportunities%20for%20my%20children.%20But%20joining%20Foreka%20changed%20everything.%20They%20offered%20fair%20prices%20for%20my%20mustard%20seeds%2C%20which%20boosted%20my%20income%2C%20and%20trained%20me%20to%20operate%20machines%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20steady%20job.%20Now%2C%20my%20children%20are%20receiving%20an%20education%2C%20and%20one%20is%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20Veterinary%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20treated%20as%20partners%2C%20not%20just%20suppliers.%20They%20have%20a%20direct%20stake%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20ensures%20that%20they%20are%20as%20invested%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20business%20as%20we%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%2C%20building%20a%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20significant%20challenges%20as%20they%20expanded%20their%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20raise%20funds%20after%20becoming%20a%20private%20limited%20company.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20impact%20investors%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20entrepreneurship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20their%20inexperience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driven%20by%20willpower%2C%20but%20we%20had%20little%20experience%20and%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20skills.%20We%20realised%20that%20skills%20are%20developed%20through%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20mentoring%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20major%20challenge%20came%20when%20the%20trio%20encountered%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20taken%20a%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20loan%20to%20procure%20oil%20from%20farmers%2C%20and%20we%20received%20our%20first%20order%20in%20July%202022%2C%20a%20300-litre%20batch%20of%20cold-pressed%20oil.%20The%20order%20was%20valued%20around%20Rs%206-7%20lakh%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20send%20it%20to%20Noida%20in%20the%20NCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20all%20night%20packing%20and%20preparing%20the%20shipment%2