2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20sex%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20nobody%20was%20ready%20to%20employ%20me%20for%20other%20jobs.%20I%20needed%20to%20survive%2C%20and%20this%20job%20provided%20me%20with%20the%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20affirms.%20Outside%20the%20social%20stigma%2C%20her%20profession%20also%20came%20with%20serious%20health%20consequences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESexually%20transmitted%20diseases%20were%20common%20among%20sex%20workers%2C%20and%20Noori%20often%20assisted%20them%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267251%2Fvaccinate-sex-workers-transgenders-domestic-help-free-covidactioncollab-coronavirus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20medical%20help%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20one%20such%20visit%20to%20a%20hospital%2C%20Noori%20saw%20a%20poster%20on%20HIV%20and%20AIDS%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20get%20tested%2C%20and%20stating%20that%20there%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20the%20disease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20handle%2010%20to%2015%20clients%20daily%20and%20I%20wondered%20why%20this%20was%20such%20a%20deadly%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9COn%20July%2022%2C%201987%2C%20I%20was%20the%20second%20person%20to%20be%20tested%20positive%20for%20HIV%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20spending%20some%20quality%20time%20with%20the%20kids%20at%20the%20shelter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FTBI-featured-image-8_11zon-1736169095-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20has%20invested%20in%20a%20space%20worth%20Rs%203%20crore%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20told%20Noori%20that%20she%20would%20live%20only%20for%20a%20year%20or%20two.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20disheartened%20for%20a%20week%2C%20but%20Dr%20Usha%20Raghavan%20came%20to%20my%20tiny%20house%20searching%20for%20me%2C%20provided%20counselling%20and%20educated%20me%20about%20the%20condition%2C%20which%20changed%20my%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20adopted%20three%20kids%20from%20a%20commercial%20sex%20worker%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20live%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%2C%20who%20saw%20Noori%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20financially%2C%20secured%20her%20a%20job%20at%20the%20STD%20department%20in%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Hospital.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learnt%20to%20retrieve%20blood%2C%20dress%20wounds%2C%20and%20identify%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Raghavan%20provided%20a%20monthly%20amount%20of%20Rs%20800%2C%20which%20was%20essential%20for%20my%20survival.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%20also%20encouraged%20her%20to%20join%20the%20Community%20Action%20Network%20as%20an%20outreach%20worker.%20Despite%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20HIV%2C%20Noori%20faced%20severe%20isolation%20and%20discrimination.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20pig%E2%80%99s%20fodder%20to%20eat%20as%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20a%20disheartening%20experience%20during%20an%20outreach%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20HIV%20often%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20surrounding%20both%20my%20transgender%20identity%20and%20HIV%20status%20led%20many%20to%20fear%20and%20ostracise%20me%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%2C%20who%20were%20also%20living%20with%20the%20virus.%20I%20hated%20it%20when%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20disease%2C%20ill-treat%20their%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20treated%20us%20like%20dogs%2C%20throwing%20stones%20at%20us%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20transmitted%20like%20the%20flu%20virus.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Noori%20continued%20undeterred%2C%20raising%20awareness%20about%20HIV%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20compassionate%20treatment%20of%20all%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%