nt%2C%20in%201998%2C%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20Sarbeswar.%20From%20there%2C%20he%20began%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20department%2C%20learning%20about%20agriculture%2C%20improving%20yields%2C%20finding%20ways%20to%20increase%20his%20profits%20each%20season%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20intercropping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVenturing%20into%20integrated%20farming%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20areca%20nut%20crop%20takes%20years%20to%20start%20yielding.%20Even%20when%20they%20do%2C%20the%20yields%20are%20often%20not%20as%20high.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20depending%20solely%20on%20one%20crop%2C%20I%20had%20learnt%20about%20intercropping%20and%20how%20it%20could%20be%20helpful%2C%20even%20necessary%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sarbeswar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20number%20of%20people%20in%20a%20family%20increases%2C%20the%20land%20keeps%20getting%20smaller.%20To%20survive%2C%20we%20need%20to%20grow%20multiple%20crops%20each%20year%2C%20and%20have%20harvests%20in%20every%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20initially%20grew%20arecanuts%2C%20but%20over%20time%2C%20added%20three%20to%20four%20more%20crops%20like%20bananas%20and%20turmeric%2C%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20income%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20profits%20improved%20a%20lot.%20I%20kept%20trying%20new%20farming%20methods%20and%20realised%20that%20intercropping%20was%20the%20key%20to%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-